{"id": "1196296512154652743", "channel_id": "1189847836758646895", "type": 0, "author_id": "595205741351010316", "author_name": "moyuliuli", "author_bot": false, "content": "这周的造物也还行，攻击回盾+残余盾加触手伤害和力量", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T03:35:14.612000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189847836758646895", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海阵容的使用心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1196296895384015059", "channel_id": "1189847836758646895", "type": 0, "author_id": "595205741351010316", "author_name": "moyuliuli", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果你能拿到苦痛圣腕，就是那个上限-1但是所有触手额外攻击一次的遗物", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T03:36:45.981000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189847836758646895", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海阵容的使用心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174179716706619494"]}
