{"id": "1196297247181242488", "channel_id": "1189847836758646895", "type": 0, "author_id": "595205741351010316", "author_name": "moyuliuli", "author_bot": false, "content": "刚打了一次靠遗物一回合叠加了90点触手伤害", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T03:38:09.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189847836758646895", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海阵容的使用心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1196297661628813333", "channel_id": "1189847836758646895", "type": 0, "author_id": "595205741351010316", "author_name": "moyuliuli", "author_bot": false, "content": "顺便我收回之前的奥瑞塔不适合开狂气爆发的言论，这周奥瑞塔三次启灵了，然后今天的商店遗物一般我就把法洛斯觉醒了，结果才第五回合牌库20张腺体分裂……严重污染牌库，要是不开爆发撕掉的话后面很容易暴毙", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T03:39:48.668000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189847836758646895", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海阵容的使用心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1196382923704766534", "channel_id": "1189847836758646895", "type": 0, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "这个周的造物可以极大的拉高下限，毕竟高频率的触手可以触发大量的盾，但是上限的话不是很足，打60级深潜都很勉强的样子", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T09:18:36.731000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189847836758646895", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海阵容的使用心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1196410003943338034", "channel_id": "1189847836758646895", "type": 0, "author_id": "595205741351010316", "author_name": "moyuliuli", "author_bot": false, "content": "要配合增加触手攻击次数，临时触手数量的东西，特别是那个所有触手回合后额外攻击一次的", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T11:06:13.163000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189847836758646895", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海阵容的使用心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1196420385227423744", "channel_id": "1189847836758646895", "type": 0, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "是的，圣腕可以很好的吃到本周的造物福利，不过目前来看在build未成型的情况下很容易在高深潜（60以上）的前中期道中吃不消，暂时还没很好的办法去挑战更高级别的深潜。得看一下后续的遗物刷新情况", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T11:47:28.254000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1189847836758646895", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海阵容的使用心得", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1196356931191832677", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1196286665900183594", "channel_id": "1195148765145866241", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "字太多了\n加上有裝飾\n重點資訊沒有加強閱讀引導\n導致整個畫面很雜亂看不到重點在哪", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T02:56:07.082000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1195148765145866241", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "索蕾尔角色全攻略1", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1174179734373019748", "1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1196306342416220161", "channel_id": "1195148765145866241", "type": 19, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "（小聲的跟貓貓頭佬說一些對於攻略圖文的想法\n\n1.因為大部分人使用手機閱讀的習慣是由上往下，所以保持每張圖片的文字在統一區域會比較能讓人順利閱讀。\n\n2.考慮到每個人的手機螢幕亮度跟對比度的差異，文字與背景的顏色太過相近或是對比太大的話會造成閱讀時的不適感。\n\n3.字體的種類、大小、間距跟上述顏色的情況綜合起來後，有點難以閱讀。\n\n4.雖然裝飾可以讓內容版面顯得更華麗有趣，但是有些裝飾反而讓他人在閱讀時分心了，並遮蓋住原文的內容。\n\n最後還是感謝貓貓頭佬寫一篇圖文並茂的攻略，儘管我還沒抽到紅夫人Orz", "timestamp": "2024-01-15T04:14:18.329000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-15T04:15:04.683000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1181971546496061540"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1195148765145866241", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1195148765145866241", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "索蕾尔角色全攻略1", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1174179734373019748", "1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
